snippet.title: The Family Man S3 - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Manoj Bajpayee, Jaideep Ahlawat | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

Created by: Raj & DK

Directed by: Raj & DK, Suman Kumar, Tusshar Seyth
Produced by: Raj & DK

I Became a Prisoner on the Unstable SMP

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of the music I use is by AZALI so check him out!)

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe / Unstable SMP that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, official enderal soundtrack, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)

snippet.title: Super Car Race Motu Patlu Ki Non Stop Comedy Sab Hue Lotpot üòÇ | Motu Patlu | Kiddie Land
snippet.description:
Motu Patlu shamil hote hain ek super car race mein jahan har gadhi car, rocket car aur funny gadget cars unka intezaar kar rahi hoti hain! Motu ki hungry driving aur Patlu ka super tension full-on comedy create kar deti hai. Race ke beech John aur uski gang bhi cheating karne ki koshish karte hain, par Motu Patlu ki masti aur teamwork sabko hila kar rakh deti hai. High-speed stunts, nonstop comedy aur dhamal se bharpur ek zabardast adventure shuru ho jata hai!


Show Name: Motu Patlu
Directed By: Suhas D. Kadav
Written By: Niraj Vikram
Original language: Hindi


#motupatlu  #furfurinagar #kidsanimation

About Motu Patlu:
-----------------------------
Motu and Patlu, two best friends living in the bustling town of Furfuri Nagar, often find themselves in hilarious and troublesome situations. Motu loves eating samosas, which give him bursts of energy, while Patlu is the smarter and slimmer friend who tries to keep Motu out of trouble. Despite their constant troubles, they are usually saved by luck and the help of their good friends like Ghasita Ram, the ever-experienced but often unhelpful companion; Inspector Chingam, the proud but sometimes clumsy police officer; and Dr. Jhatka, the eccentric scientist whose inventions often create more chaos than solutions. Together, they make Furfuri Nagar a lively and fun-filled place full of adventure and laughter.
